languages.text: "Да пошла она! Мы ее приютили, защитили, с родней ее возились... Давайте отнесем ее тело Тервантьясу, пусть воскресит ее, а мы еще раз убьем!"
"She deserved what she got! We took her in, protected her, and even got involved with her kin... I say we take her body to Tervantias, have him resurrect her, and then kill her again!"

languages.text: “她活该！我们收留了她，保护了她，甚至为了她，卷入到她的族人那堆破烂事里面……要我说，我们就该把她的尸体带到特万提亚斯那里，让他把她复活，然后再杀她一遍！”
languages.original_text: "She deserved what she got! We took her in, protected her, and even got involved with her kin... I say we take her body to Tervantias, have him resurrect her, and then kill her again!"

traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion

languages.text: « Elle n'a eu que ce qu'elle méritait ! On l'a acceptée parmi nous, on l'a protégée, et on a même eu affaire à ses semblables... On devrait demander à Tervantias de la ressusciter pour pouvoir la tuer de nouveau ! »
languages.original_text: "She deserved what she got! We took her in, protected her, and even got involved with her kin... I say we take her body to Tervantias, have him resurrect her, and then kill her again!"

languages.text: «¡Se lo tenía bien merecido! La acogimos, la protegimos e incluso nos involucramos con su gente... ¡Sugiero que llevemos su cadáver a Tervantias, hagamos que la resucite y después volvamos a matarla!».

languages.text: 「ユリエットはそれだけのことをしたの！私たちの仲間に入れて、守って、キンとの争いにまで巻き込まれて…彼女の遺体はテルヴァンティアスに渡しましょう、蘇生させて、また殺すのよ！」
languages.original_text: "She deserved what she got! We took her in, protected her, and even got involved with her kin... I say we take her body to Tervantias, have him resurrect her, and then kill her again!"

traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion

languages.text: "Sie hat bekommen, was sie verdient hat! Wir haben sie aufgenommen, sie beschützt, sie sogar mit ihren Verwandten zusammengeführt ... Ich sage, wir bringen ihre Leiche zu Tervantias, damit er sie wiederbelebt, und dann töten wir sie erneut!"
